{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"attributeType","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/attributeType","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>该属性指定目标属性和它相对应的值处于哪个命名空间里。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>动画属性目标属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td>CSS | XML | <strong>auto</strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/animate.html#AttributeTypeAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>这个属性可取下列值之一：</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"css\">CSS</dt>\n <dd>指定<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/attributeName\">attributeName</a></code>的值是一个 CSS 属性名。</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">&nbsp;</dt>\n <dt id=\"xml\">XML</dt>\n <dd>指定<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/attributeName\">attributeName</a></code>的值是一个 XML 属性名，在目标元素的默认 XML 命名空间里。</dd>\n <dt id=\"auto\">auto</dt>\n <dd>编译器将把<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/attributeName\">attributeName</a></code>匹配到目标元素的一个属性。用户代理先搜索 CSS 属性列表以找出一个匹配的属性名，如果找不到，再为这个元素搜索默认 XML 命名空间。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>attributeType</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animate&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animateColor&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateTransform\"><code>&lt;animateTransform&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"attributeType","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"attributeType","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/attributetype","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/attributetype/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/attributeType","title":"attributeType"}],"pageTitle":"attributeType - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}